title: Mindless Self Indulgence - On It (Remix Stemz)
description:
Welcome to the MSI "On It" remix contest.
This download contains three vocal "stems" -- and hey, we&#039;re not even charging you for &#039;em like SOME bands. The files are lossless WAVs and contain primary vocals and vocal effects for the song, however, there&#039;s no backing music.

Here&#039;s where you come in...download this and create your own backing tracks/remix! The band will listen to the remixes, and the winner shall appear on the next Mindless Self Indulgence release (after "If" of course). Remix deadline is April 28th, 11:59PM EST.

Please see the text file (included in the download with the stems) for additional rules and information.

The new album by Mindless Self Indulgence, "If"...out April 29th in North America (worldwide release info on our MySpace). Keep tabs on mindlessselfindulgence.com /for LOTS more in the coming days, weeks, and months.

Have fun, and good luck you remixing little fucks.
